Argentina beat Ecuador 2-1 at the MetLife Stadium in New Jersey on Tuesday night . 
  Sergio Aguero opened the scoring for Argentina in the first half . 
  Miller Bolanos equalised for Ecuador in the second half . 
  Javier Pastore scored the winner in the 58th minute . 
  Gerardo Martino's side are preparing for the Copa America . 
  Lionel Messi missed the game with a foot injury . 
 